or normalizes path and injects JWT\n500: - [x] ModifyResponse adds session header\n501: - [x] ErrorHandler maps errors to HTTP codes (502/504)\n502: - [x] JWTManager with RSA key generation\n503: - [x] GenerateToken with RS256, 5m expiration\n504: - [x] TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret placeholder\n505: - [x] concurrencyLimitMiddleware with semaphore\n506: - [x] 429 returned when overloaded\n507: - [x] handleHealthLive returns 200 {\"status\":\"alive\"}\n508: - [x] handleHealthReady checks sessionManager availability\n509: - [x] handleInvoke proxies to sandbox with activity tracking\n510: - [x] Activity timestamp updated before and after proxy\n511: - [x] Error types implement APIStatus interface\n512: - [x] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL required for SessionManager\n513: - [x] AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE with default \"default\"\n514: - [x] Constants defined (rsaKeySize, jwtExpiration, IdentitySecretName)\n515: - [x] Unit tests for all components\n516: - [x] Mock implementations for testing\n517: \n518: ---\n519: \n520: ## Files Modified/Created\n521: \n522: | File | Status | Description |\n523: |------|--------|-------------|\n524: | `pkg/router/errors.go` | Created | Error types with APIStatus interface |\n525: | `pkg/router/errors_test.go` | Created | Error types unit tests |\n526: | `pkg/router/config.go` | Created | Config struct and DefaultConfig |\n527: | `pkg/router/config_test.go` | Created | Config unit tests |\n528: | `pkg/router/doc.go` | Created | Interface definitions (Store, Logger, SessionManager, APIStatus) |\n529: | `pkg/router/jwt.go` | Created | JWTManager implementation with RS256 |\n530: | `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` | Created | JWT unit tests |\n531: | `pkg/router/session_manager.go` | Created | SessionManager implementation |\n532: | `pkg/router/session_manager_test.go` | Created | SessionManager unit tests with MockStore |\n533: | `pkg/router/middleware.go` | Created | Concurrency, logging, recovery middleware |\n534: | `pkg/router/middleware_test.go` | Created | Mid